          <h3 class="tool-name">Replit</h3>
          <p class="tool-desc">A browser-based IDE that lets you code, run, and deploy applications without any local setup. Perfect for prototyping, collaboration, and learning on the fly.</p>
          <a href="https://replit.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="tool-link">Visit Website ↗</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="tool-card">
        <img src="https://kiro.dev/favicon.ico" alt="Kiro" class="tool-logo" onerror="this.style.display='none'" />
