          <h3 class="tool-name">Kiro</h3>
          <p class="tool-desc">An AI-powered development environment built on VS Code. Kiro brings autonomous coding agents, spec-driven development, and intelligent hooks directly into your workflow.</p>
          <a href="https://kiro.dev" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="tool-link">Visit Website ↗</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="tool-card">
        <img src="https://cursor.sh/favicon.ico" alt="Cursor AI" class="tool-logo" onerror="this.style.display='none'" />
