          <h3 class="tool-name">Vercel</h3>
          <p class="tool-desc">Deploy frontend applications in seconds with zero configuration. The platform of choice for Next.js, React, and Astro projects with global CDN and instant rollbacks.</p>
          <a href="https://vercel.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="tool-link">Visit Website ↗</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="tool-card">
        <img src="https://ghost.org/favicon.ico" alt="Ghost CMS" class="tool-logo" onerror="this.style.display='none'" />
        <div class="tool-info">
          <h3 class="tool-name">Ghost CMS</h3>
          <p class="tool-desc">A modern, open-source publishing platform built for professional writers and developers. Powers newsletters, blogs, and membership sites with a clean API-first architecture.</p>
          <a href="https://ghost.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="tool-link">Visit Website ↗</a>
        </div>
      </div>

