        <div class="tool-info">
          <h3 class="tool-name">StudentChakra</h3>
          <p class="tool-desc">India's leading platform for student opportunities — internships, hackathons, scholarships, and projects. An essential resource for building your career while still in college.</p>
          <a href="https://studentchakra.in" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="tool-link">Visit Website ↗</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="tool-card">
        <img src="https://hack2skill.com/favicon.ico" alt="Hack2Skill" class="tool-logo" onerror="this.style.display='none'" />
        <div class="tool-info">
          <h3 class="tool-name">Hack2Skill</h3>
          <p class="tool-desc">A platform connecting student developers with national hackathons, coding challenges, and innovation competitions — the fastest path to building a real project portfolio.</p>
          <a href="https://hack2skill.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="tool-link">Visit Website ↗</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="tool-card">
        <img src="https://antigravity.dev/favicon.ico" alt="Antigravity" class="tool-logo" onerror="this.style.display='none'" />
        <div class="tool-info">
          <h3 class="tool-name">Antigravity</h3>
          <p class="tool-desc">A community and platform for developers who want to build ambitious projects. Focused on helping developers break through barriers and ship impactful software.</p>
          <a href="https://antigravity.dev" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="tool-link">Visit Website ↗</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="tool-card">
        <div class="tool-logo tool-logo-text">API</div>
