      <div class="lesson-card">
        <div class="lesson-number">02</div>
        <h3 class="lesson-title">Practice Every Day</h3>
        <p class="lesson-desc">Consistency beats intensity. Thirty minutes of daily coding compounds into mastery faster than sporadic marathon sessions. The streak is the skill.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="lesson-card">
